__SqlaTable__.sql:
/* Most often traded collections? */
SELECT
slug,
SUM(volume) total_volume,
SUM(volume_eth) total_volume_eth
FROM collections_daily cagg
INNER JOIN collections c ON cagg.collection_id = c.id
INNER JOIN assets a ON a.id = cagg.most_expensive_nft_id
GROUP BY cagg.collection_id, slug
ORDER BY total_volume DESC

/* Assets caggs + info */ SELECT bucket, a.id AS asset_id, a.name AS asset_name, c.slug AS collection_slug, mean_price, median_price, volume, volume_eth, open_price, high_price, low_price, close_price, '' AS nft_image FROM assets_daily cagg INNER JOIN collections c ON cagg.collection_id = c.id INNER JOIN assets a ON a.id = cagg.asset_id
